fr.sii.ogham.core.mimetype

Class TikaProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sii.ogham.core.mimetype.TikaProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MimeTypeProvider

    public class TikaProvider
extends Object
implements MimeTypeProvider
    Mime Type detection based on Apache Tika. This library is very complete and up-to-date. It is also able to parse documents but this is not useful in our case.
    Author:
